@node Version_History "Version History"

@{line}@{u}Version History@{uu}@{line}

@{b}1.5  4-Oct-99@{ub}, sixth public release
@{lindent 4}@{pari -2}@{par}· Corrected number of sectors in
@{"mount files" link Mount_Files} for 1.3GB 3½" disks. They actually have
605846 user sectors. Further independent confirmation of this would be
appreciated.@{par}
· Moved stuff about cleaning drive and disks to the new
@{"maintenance" link Maintenance} section.@{par}
· Added warning about using the correct type of cleaning cartridge for cleaning
the drive lens.@{par}
· Mention that Fujitsu's latest 3½" drives have a seek time of 23ms.@{par}
· Changed BlocksPerTrack and HighCyl values of PC Superfloppy and FFS, SFS
540MB @{"mount files" link Mount_Files} so that HighCyl < 32768. This should
have no consequence other than to improve compatibility with old, badly written
disk editor tools (e.g. the ProjectD EditorTool).@{par}
· Various other minor changes.@{pard}@{par}

